They crash against the window! Battering their bodies to a bloody pulp against the glass! They are trying to get in!....They want to get in!

The noise is unbearable! Wings beating a tattoo of death on the window! Screams of their frenzied attack shatter my mind!...
The window becomes encrusted with bits of bone sticking to the smears of blood!
Then....they go! In a moment they dart away into the shadows of the night!
I fall back into bed, mentally drained.
It is morning at last! I stir through my slumber.. I have slept as though drugged... no more dreams or apparitions..perhaps it was all a dream..ah well! I hastily arrive and dress. Today should see me to my destination!
