I am outside the hotel, on the alpine track. My way lies North, high into the mountains........
The driver looks down at me.

"Sir, we must get an early start, if we are to reach your rendezvous before nightfall. My team is fast. Do you wish to travel with me?"

I think for a moment...

"Please sir, time is passing. Yes or No?"

