The carriage pulls up, the horses blowing hard!
The coachman rummages under his cloak. He produces a document.
"This coach has been booked for an English gentleman. I'm to take him part way to the castle."
He looks toward the mountain through narrowing eyes and shudders.....
"I am to take him and no other. If you are he, please state your name....."
> jonathan harker

> jonathan harker

He checks his list, then looks down at me.

"Ya! This is so!.... Please now board the coach so we may be on our way."

I board and make myself comfortable. Little did I realise when I left England that such an almost medieval way of life still existed in the world today. This land steeped in superstition is a new experience for me. Now, on the final leg of my journey I ponder on the events of the night before. Try to determine dreams from reality...

I wonder what new adventures await me.... what terrors..... I look through the window at the distant mountain.... huge, silent..... I shudder..... I see the spires of the castle!

The driver looks down at me.
"Sir, I must ensure that I have the right passenger. Please state your name, which must tally with my list."
PART II: THE ARRIVAL

The end of this day will see me to my destination!
Soon we are high in the mountains. The views are stunning!
Occasionally I see the castle, high up, watching through the cloud. Watching? Why should I feel that? Castles don't watch!
.....Looking again I gain the impression that it is built in the style of a grand French chateau... tall towers and pinnacles...

The coach rattles on with an urgency I find disarming....

I am sitting on the coach, on the way to Castle Dracula!
A woman is sitting opposite. She is dressed in black... a shawl of black lace covers her head, falling loosely over her shoulders. Her face is barely visible....

> look around

> look around

A woman is sitting opposite. She is dressed in black... a shawl of black lace covers her head, falling loosely over her shoulders. Her face is barely visible....
> examine eyes

> examine eyes

In those deep pools I see images yet to come!.....A dark room.....
I see three people in white shrouds, clamouring over a bed in the corner...... they are young women and giggle intermittently.. not the laugher of innocent youth, but of something much more sinister.... there is someone in the bed....I hear noises.... there must be a dog here. Yes, a dog, chewing a piece of meat?
They stand, their backs toward me... then they slowly turn.. god no! Their faces! Smiling but with the malevolence of Satan!...
Their deathly white faces are running in blood!
Hissing hysterically, they reach for me!!!

> close eyes

> close eyes

I break the trance! Everything slips back into focus. All assume a reassuring reality. She looks at me knowingly with a faint smile.

 "Sir, the future cannot be seen for certain...Just possibilities. Take this to help you in your endevours."

So saying, she hangs me a silver cross on a thong.

> wear cross

> wear cross

I put the thong over my head and tuck the cross into my shirt.
