Night is almost here as we stop at the last rendezvous. We are at the borgo pass, where I am to meet the count's coach....
Suddenly a coach pulls up beside us! It's big black horses tossing their manes.
The driver is clad in a big cloak, thrown across his face and over his shoulder.
His wide brimmed hat is pulled over his eyes to add to his anonymity. He peers into the coach, then calls out in a hard but surprisingly cultured tone,

"Are you going to visit Count Dracula?"
