I walk to the sofa in the dressing room and sit. It is peaceful here.. I watch the moonlight playing on dust, dancing in it's glow...it swirls and twists...
I drift into a dreamy state of calm... the dust dances...gaining volume, forming three seperate columns. Then.... slowly, three female forms materialise.
They are young and pretty...I'm glad they are here. They drift round me, laughing. The laughter of summer, gay, romantic.

Their beauty beguiles me... I am totally entranced. One leans forward to kiss me. I close my eyes, awaiting the pleasures to come.
I feel her lips on my neck.
A shudder coarses through me!
Then, a little sting. I revel in her affection. Then a half remembered dream.. three women round a bed... I open my eyes.

She lifts her head and laughs a mocking laugh... her lips curl back to reveal her teeth..once white, now bloodstained and streaked..teeth? No! These are fangs and they drip with my blood!!
