"I will reach England Jonathan Harker, and your kinsman will pay for the pain you have inflicted upon me! Oh how they will pay!"

Should I reach safety I must write to England of the boxes. My friends much destroy them! They truly must!!!

 PART 3 : THE HUNT

My name is John Seward. I am a doctor of the mind and own an asylum here in Purfleet.
The grounds are extensive. Adjacent is the Carfax estate, the house of which has stood derelict for years. Renfield, one of my patients, escaped last week. He has absconded before but the police always catch him, so no need to worry. He is harmless. Spends his time feeding flies to spiders, then eating the spiders... says that if one spider has eaten fifty flies, then he will absorb the strength of the flies by eating the spider!
Ah well....the logic of a madman.
I am in my study. A somewhat crowded repository of books and records. My desk is strewn with notes. To the West is the hall, while East is my bedroom.

