The days pass eventfully.
Van Helsing has arrived. We are now sure we are dealing with a case of vampirism! The remains of animals have been found, mutilated. This is clearly the work of Renfield. There are also the attacks on local children.
These either disappear, or are found weak with two rat like bikes on their neck! Renfield has not been caught yet. He also has been seen in the woods to the west, screaming death to me! Dracula has not been seen yet, so there is much to do. Renfield must be caught first. He is an immediate problem!

