"You!....You attempt to contaminate my resting places...You are a fool to think you can do battle with me! For this you will die in an ecstacy of pain!"

He starts toward me....then stops.
He looks down at the garlic flowers.

"Ha! So you think you can stop me with weeds? By tomorrow they will have lost their power....I still have one box hidden! So make the most of what little time you have left. Ha! Ha!"

Then he slips away into the shadows!
